---
// About.astro – Sobre Mí section
---

<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title"><span class="gradient-text">Sobre Mí</span></h2>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Card 1 – Bio -->
      <div class="glass-card animate-in about-bio-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
            <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Perfil Profesional</h3>
        <p>
          Soy Ana Patricia Hernández Lara, desarrolladora de software con más de 4 años de experiencia construyendo soluciones tecnológicas reales. Mi pasión es transformar ideas en productos funcionales que resuelven problemas concretos.
        </p>
        <p>
          He trabajado en proyectos completos desde cero: aplicaciones móviles publicadas en Google Play y App Store, sistemas de punto de venta e inventario, plataformas administrativas, APIs REST y sitios web corporativos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 – Education -->
      <div class="glass-card animate-in">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z" />
            <path d="M6 12v5c0 1.1 2.7 3 6 3s6-1.9 6-3v-5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Formación Académica</h3>

        <div class="edu-item">
          <span class="edu-degree">Ingeniería en Sistemas Computacionales</span>
          <span class="edu-school">Universidad Autónoma de Tamaulipas</span>
          <span class="edu-period">2021 – 2026 | Estudios concluidos</span>
        </div>

        <div class="edu-item">
          <span class="edu-degree">Técnico en Programación</span>
          <span class="edu-school">CETis 109</span>
          <span class="edu-period">2018 – 2021</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 – Achievements -->
      <div class="glass-card animate-in">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6" />
            <path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18" />
            <path d="M4 22h16" />
            <path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20.24 7 22" />
            <path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20.24 17 22" />
            <path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Logros</h3>

        <ul class="achievements-list">
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="achievement-icon">
              <path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6" />
              <path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18" />
              <path d="M4 22h16" />
              <path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20.24 7 22" />
              <path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20.24 17 22" />
              <path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z" />
            </svg>
            <span>ICPC Grand Final Mexico 2024 y 2025</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="achievement-icon">
              <path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6" />
              <path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18" />
              <path d="M4 22h16" />
              <path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20.24 7 22" />
              <path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20.24 17 22" />
              <path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z" />
            </svg>
            <span>ICPC Local 2022, 2023, 2024 y 2025</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="achievement-icon">
              <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2" />
              <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18" />
            </svg>
            <span>App publicada en Google Play y App Store</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  /* ── Bio paragraphs ── */
  .about-bio-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .about-bio-card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* ── Card icon ── */
  .card-icon {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-primary) 12%, transparent);
  }

  /* ── Card headings ── */
  .glass-card h3 {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }

  /* ── Education items ── */
  .edu-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .edu-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .edu-degree {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .edu-school {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
  }

  .edu-period {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  /* ── Achievements list ── */
  .achievements-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.65rem;
  }

  .achievements-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(96, 114, 90, 0.04);
    transition: background 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;
  }

  .achievement-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .achievements-list li:hover {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-primary) 8%, transparent);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .about-bio-card {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .about-bio-card {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }
  }
</style>
